Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I must take you for a check-up today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it's pointless,\Nno matter how many times you come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I'm coming\Nall the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody asked you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You stubborn, cranky woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.09,0:00:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking, you quack doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen a doctor since I was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm doing just fine as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.23,0:00:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-Just get out of here!\N-Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, we have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Schumann!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The drunkard Fink got hit on the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy who carried him in\Nis treating him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who was passing by\Nis checking his injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When I told him you were out\Non a house call, he just…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you let him treat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I tried to stop him,\Nbut he said the patient might choke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So he asked me to give him\Nfirst aid at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.\NHe left without leaving a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he did write something on the chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"The patient said not to take him\Nto a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because he had no money."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"So please use this money to pay\Nfor his medical fees."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did the guy look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He was Asian, and he had a boy with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… What should we do\Nabout Mr. Fink's treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:01:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave him on the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But that man only did first aid…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't just first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't have you keep\Nfollowing me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot stay in one place,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so you cannot go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-I have a friend.\N-Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you the one who meddled at my clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware that Fink is\Na penniless drunkard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never considered taking\Nmoney from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably some elite doctor\Nfrom a famous hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,making yourself feel good\Nwith some charity work on your vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey.\N-Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go, Dieter.\N-What's up? Are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Not at all.\N-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me when I'm talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize, but we are in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fink got involved in a hit-and-run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That drunkard Fink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for any eyewitnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dr. Schumann.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Fink's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive enough. I'm more worried\Nabout his drinking problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Dr. Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He was my junior at my old college.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped by our village\Nduring his vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Chang? Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He treated Fink for me today,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,since I was on a house call.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you know\Nwhere I went today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Heinz, I was at your mother Petra's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom's?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You should tell her to come to the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She may need treatment immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible. That stubborn woman\Nwon't listen to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like it's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! My mom won't die that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, after raising me to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she has any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra has her own life to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you make up that lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just to thank you for saving Fink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Without your swift treatment,\Nhe might have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned white as a sheet\Nwhen you saw the policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,At least now, I'm sure you're not\Nan elite doctor from a famous hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Repay me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a way for you to repay me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cast is a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll hurt a bit, but please bear with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be able to take it off\Nafter two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I made some nice apple brandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that when you're injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After you're healed,\NI can drink with you all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You are making good progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,After five days, you can work on the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Mr. Schöne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, please take some potatoes\Nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They are very tasty this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come by next time with my truck\Nand fill it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help.\NMy specialism is internal medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to do as much as I can\Noutside my field,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's hard doing it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This village doesn't have much,\Nbut it's nice and peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You are well-loved by the people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And you genuinely love them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost that feeling a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me to one more house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know when to give up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll come back\Nas many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be the same every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get out of here, quack doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the mother of that policeman.\NShe got sick during farm work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to take her to the clinic,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but she said she was fine and came back\Nbefore we got to the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worrisome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I try to convince her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be the same, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still dawdling about out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where I dawdle is none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. If you keep yelling like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody would want to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking you to the clinic,\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't lose my reason for living!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah… No…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to lose someone\NI love to argue with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And… I wouldn't be able to eat\Nthe goulash she makes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, your face is all red.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please open up, Petra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Another doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless! That stubborn woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you hate doctors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They play with people's bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and they all think they're some\Nkind of god!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gods, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I wish I were a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we try our best,\Nmistakes will always happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could heal people\Nperfectly like a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I see a patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I always get nervous and hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Let us see your face, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? This smell is…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making goulash?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Do you like goulash?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like your goulash\Nis Dr. Schumann's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I've heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I made it for him,\Nhe only sat there and ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness. My shoulders hurt so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have to get dinner ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoulder pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra, can you touch your chest\Nwith your chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I can! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can fit four fingers in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that some kind of spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no… It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid it could be\Na subarachnoid hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a fax about a murder suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Make more copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your mother?\NI heard she fainted three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't die, even if you kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're within 72 hours of her first spasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much time,\Nso we need to operate immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if a helicopter would make it…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do the operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can do the surgery, please do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will lose another loved one\Nbecause of my own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you saw Kenzo Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. He must still be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Roadblocks on the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a great achievement\Nif we catch him, Heinz!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Y… Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All officers, emergency deployment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! If all goes well,\NI'll get a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heinz. A call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Heinz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom collapsed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had forced her
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to check into a national hospital\Nafter the first spasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my only hope, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As I suspected, it's a middle\Ncerebral artery bifurcation aneurysm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.\NWe don't have a surgical microscope
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or a craniotome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have cerebral artery clips,\NI can try operating without a microscope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even for you, it'll be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If her cerebral aneurysm ruptures again,\Nshe might not be able to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is happening again,\Nand it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dr. Schumann?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not talking like someone who's\Ntaking care of an entire village alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can only do our best\Nfor the patient as doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy. Is Dr. Schumann inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's doing a surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Surgery? On my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't send her to the city hospital,\Nbut he's doing it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Tenma is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say "Tenma"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How are her blood pressure and pulse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure is 126/84\Nand pulse rate is 88.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't even have a craniotome,\Nbut he opened her skull so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see,\Nwe're operating on your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with that gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands up, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of a surgery.\NAre you trying to kill your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who's trying to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy has been running away\Nbecause he's a murder suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed a man in Heidelberg,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's a suspect for the serial murders\Nof middle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd find him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful that my mom\Nhas given me this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on and put your hands up.\NOtherwise, I'll shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a sterile operating room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bringing in germs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If infection enters this room, your mother\Ncould get meningitis and it'll be fatal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, hurry and stop the surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to get your mother killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother is suffering\Nfrom a subarachnoid hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She first collapsed three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't do the surgery now,\Nit'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my mom a hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to use my mom as a hostage\Nand run away from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cerebral artery clips and forceps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the clips and forceps!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Y… Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone hurt my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Petra is your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But what have you done for her\Nin the past five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you moved into the town,\Ndid you ever visit her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,After she brought you up all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,what have you done for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! People you cherish\Nwill be gone someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still remember the taste of\Nyour mother's goulash?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, Petra still makes\Nyour share out of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I eat the leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious, just excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is trying to save your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's doing everything he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you still want to taste that goulash,\Nget out of here quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it'd be fine\Nsince Tenma is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure is 140/86\Nand pulse rate is 82.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Vital signs are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Pionier, you should\Nget some rest as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But you two are…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.\NYou go ahead and have some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'll go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, you should sleep as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You did that difficult surgery\Nfrom beginning to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to keep watch, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her get better,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you can propose to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about,\Npropose to my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I thought you were asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I sleep before I take him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that. What did he mean?\NDoctor, are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the kind of man\Nwho can propose to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:18:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I never cared to talk to the patient\Nwhen I was in the university hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I only thought about how to secure\Nmy position in the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wrote papers for the director\Nto get into his faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, I married\Nthe director's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even afterwards,\NI followed the road to career success.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I never paid any attention to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I actually looked at her,\NI would've noticed something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was a real doctor…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She had suffered from cold-like symptoms\Nfor a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd paid more attention,\NI would've caught it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was liver failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In her final moments, she said…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have finally looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no right to love anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You do look at people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been watching over everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you did, Petra is saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still taking him away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This man who risked his own life\Nto save your mother's?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still think he's a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Heinz!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Heinz. The chief, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I'm sorry. It was someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call off the roadblock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The man I saw wasn't Tenma.\NIt was a man called Dr. Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I mistook him because he's Asian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry. Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor at the national hospital\Nwas surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose he never thought\Nhe'd see such amazing treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,done in a rural clinic like ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to let\Nthe young doctor go like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to treat him to something good,\Nbut he's left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe in this village!\NYou don't have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Schumann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, don't you like it here as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I guess this village\Nmight be good for you, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just for Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We can protect you from the police\Nif you stay in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of the people\Nhere with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This village needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay here,\Nwe can save so many lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let us work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Save many lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have… to kill a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you mean, Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not someone who's capable of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You work so hard to save\Nthe lives of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, he is leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dieter, go ahead.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're with Tenma,\Nhe won't stray from his path.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out for Tenma, okay?
